            <%= image_tag "temp/img-divya.png" %>
          </div> <!-- /photo -->
          <div class="testimonial__text">
            <p>Upon our initial meeting, our Property Pros representative asked us some very pertinent questions about how we live and what we wanted to accomplish.  We also gave him our wish list and ideas about how we wanted the space to function.  He really pulled it all together, and we are so grateful for what they have done.   Not only is our new finished lower level gorgeous, but functional and warm.&rdquo;.</p>
